# Real Audio Integration

## Goal Description
Use the existing [.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/e1.wav) files for audio instead of synthetic sine waves.

## User Review Required
- **Missing Drums**: If no drum files are found, I will keep using synthetic drums.
- **Piano Mapping**: Mapping [c1.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/c1.wav) to the `C3` virtual key (assuming user just wants *some* sound).

## Proposed Changes
### [ar_studio.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/ar_studio.py)
- **AudioEngine**:
    - Load [c1.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/c1.wav), [d1.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/d1.wav) etc. from [sounds/](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/ar_studio.py#57-73).
    - Map keys:
        - `C3` -> [sounds/c1.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/c1.wav)
        - `C#3` -> [sounds/c1s.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/c1s.wav)
        - ...
    - **Drums**:
        - Use synthetic if no files.

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Run [ar_studio.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/ar_studio.py).
- Play piano -> Hear recorded samples.
- Play drums -> Hear synthetic/samples.
